Charles Archibald Chubb, 2nd Baron Hayter (11 November 1871–3 March 1967) was a British businessman.
Chubb was the son of George Hayter Chubb (1848–1946), and the great grandson of Charles Chubb (1772–1845), who had founded Chubb and Sons Lock and Safe Co.
